owl:Ontology.dc:creator: Florian Kleedorfer
owl:Ontology.dc:title: Web of Needs Schema Extension
owl:Ontology.terms:abstract: This ontology contains a pair of Socket definitions automatically generated for each object property in schema.org. These sockets allow Atoms to connect to each other and thereby establish the respective relationship.

owl:NamedIndividual.rdfs:comment: An Atom `A` that specifies a Socket with this SocketDefinition derives triple `A schema:about B` when a Connection with an Atom B is established. Automatically generated from the [about](http://schema.org/about) Property of the http://schema.org vocabulary.
owl:NamedIndividual.rdfs:label: AboutSocket
